{"questionId": "369b7bb7", "correctAnswer": "C", "section": "Math", "steps": [{"title": "Substitute the value x = 3", "content": "Replace $x$ with $3$ in $$g(x) = \\sqrt{8x + 1}.$$ This gives $$g(3) = \\sqrt{8(3) + 1}.$$"}, {"title": "Compute the result", "content": "Simplify: $$g(3) = \\sqrt{25} = 5.$$ That matches choice <strong>C</strong> — <strong>C</strong> is correct.", "desmosExpressions": ["g(x)=sqrt(8x+1)"]}]}